rows.label: tlk47300161_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey, Rex! I heard you came back with
a bunch of cute girls!

rows.label: tlk47300161_01_msg0002
rows.name:
You lucky duck... Are salvagers really
that popular around Avaritia?

rows.label: tlk47300161_01_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm not doing too badly myself,
surrounded by all these old dames...
What?! Don't give me that look!

rows.label: tlk47300161_01_msg0101
rows.name:
Everything's nice and quiet here in
Iyasaki. As per usual!

rows.label: tlk47300161_01_msg0102
rows.name:
Sometimes a few stray Kapiba wander
into the village, but that's about all the
excitement we get round here.

rows.label: tlk47300161_01_msg0103
rows.name:
Probably not to the taste of a young'un
like Rex, but he'll come to
appreciate it when he's my age.

rows.label: tlk47300161_01_msg0104
rows.name:
My only grumble is that we don't have
a pub!
